Today social media play an important role in people lives. Social media can affect the way we perform, think, and/or interact with other people. Although, social media are considered an interactive tools that facilitate people's lives, they contain different types such as: Facebook, Twitter, Instagram etc. The use of Instagram put too much into the way people depict their lives through photos on social media.
The use of Instagram affects the way people interact in their daily lives. According to Dion (2016), "people who followed celebrities on Instagram started experiencing a decline in life satisfaction". Thus, the use of Instagram has an impact on people's lives especially when use it too much.
To conclude, Instagram is a tool that affects people lives and the way they interact daily. In addition, people who use Instagram especially who follow many celebrities experiencing a decline in their life satisfaction.